text: Sultana Nadira is a Bangladeshi politician who was elected as Member of 11th Jatiya Sangsad of Reserved Seats for Women. She is a politician of Bangladesh Awami League. Her late husband Golam Sabur Tulu was an MP from Barguna-2. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Awami League politicians Category:11th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Bangladeshi women in politics Category:People from Barguna district Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
